1. Project Title: Library Management System

2. Project Purpose: This system helps administrators manage the library's inventory, track user history, and oversee book details. It also allows users to browse the collection, as well as issue and return books.

3. Current Progress: It is usable and can be further improved to enhance in the future.

4. Project Functions/Features:
-  Admin: Inventory Management, User History Tracking, Book Information (add, edit and remove), Display User and Book Totals
-   User: Browse Books, View Book Information, Issue and Return Books, View Past Activity

5. Expected Pages:
-   Admin: Login, Book Management, Inventory Management, User History
-   User: Login-Signup, View Books, My Account

6. Database Used: MySQL where I store; userhistory, user_account, books and Tkinter for GUI.

7. Project Reference/Source: https://data-flair.training/blogs/library-management-system-python-project/ 
